<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="family-n">family <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fæməli/    美 /'fæməli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 家 (庭)；家人；家族；科：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a family of three
三口之家</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Lions belong to the cat family.
狮子属于猫科动物。</p></div>

<p>注: family作主语时，若指“各个家庭成员”，谓语动词用复数；若指“家庭”整体，则谓语动词用单数。如：  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My family are all fond of going to the cinema.
我全家都爱看电影。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My family is very large.
我家是个大家庭。</p></div></div>